narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I was able to focus in on a specialized area and learn about it in-depth, and I was able to steer my own research in the direction most interesting to me. I learned about hands-on applications of topics that I had previously only encountered in a purely academic setting.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think that this course is designed very well. Having a good advisor makes a huge difference, and I am grateful to have had an excellent advisor.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would absolutely recommend doing directed research!
